---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="AI Email Triage & Inbox Automation | LogicLoom Systems"
  description="Achieve Inbox Zero. We build AI agents that read, tag, and draft replies to your emails."
>
  <div x-data="{ modalOpen: false }">
    
    <section class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50/60 text-sky-700">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Workflow: Executive Ops</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        Inbox Zero. <br /> <span class="text-sky-600">Automated.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        You spend 2 hours a day sorting emails. Our AI agents read your inbox, categorize messages, draft replies, and create Jira tickets for you.
      </p>
      <button @click="modalOpen = true" class="bg-sky-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-sky-700 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-sky-500/20">
        Build My AI Agent
      </button>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-y border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">How It Works</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üì•</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">1. Analyze</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">New email arrives. n8n sends the content to GPT-4o to determine intent (Sales, Support, Spam, or Urgent).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üß†</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">2. Action</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <strong>If Support:</strong> Create Jira Ticket.<br/>
                    <strong>If Sales:</strong> Add to CRM.<br/>
                    <strong>If Spam:</strong> Delete.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">‚úçÔ∏è</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">3. Draft</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">The AI writes a context-aware reply and saves it as a "Draft" in your Gmail. You just review and hit send.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div x-show="modalOpen" style="display:none;" class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center px-4" x-transition.opacity>
      <div @click="modalOpen = false" class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
      <div class="relative bg-white w-full max-w-lg rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-4 border-b border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Book Workflow Audit</h3>
          <button @click="modalOpen = false" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-black"><i class="ph ph-x text-xl"></i></button>
        </div>
        <div class="h-[500px] w-full bg-white">
           <iframe src="https://cal.com/logicloomsystems-cal/15min?embed=true" style="width:100%;height:100%;border:none;"></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>